Description: statplot is an R package designed to simplify the creation of common statistical plots. It provides convenient wrapper functions for generating clean, publication-ready visualizations with minimal code. Whether youâ€™re exploring data, performing model diagnostics, or presenting results, statplot helps you focus on analysis rather than plotting details.
